  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/webkit\/domhtmlobjectelement-additions\ncrawled: 2025-12-12T01:25:05Z\n---\n\n# DOMHTMLObjectElement Additions\n\n**API Collection**\n\nThese additions to the `DOMHTMLObjectElement` class facilitate communication between the DOM API and WebKit.\n\n## Getting the content frame\n\n- **contentFrame**: The content frame of the element.\n\n## Related Documentation\n\n- **WebKit Objective-C Programming Guide**\n\n## Document Object Model (DOM) APIs\n\n- **DOMAbstractView**\n- **DOMAttr**\n- **DOMBlob**\n- **DOMCDATASection**\n- **DOMCharacterData**\n- **DOMComment**\n- **DOMCounter**\n- **DOMCSSCharsetRule**\n- **DOMCSSFontFaceRule**\n- **DOMCSSImportRule**\n- **DOMCSSMediaRule**\n- **DOMCSSPageRule**\n- **DOMCSSPrimitiveValue**\n- **DOMCSSRule**\n- **DOMCSSRuleList**\n\n",
